sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Frontend
    participant API as Symfony API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    User->>Frontend: Submit login form
    Frontend->>API: POST /api/login_check
    API->>DB: Verify user credentials
    DB-->>API: User found
    API-->>Frontend: 200 OK + JWT token
    Frontend->>Frontend: Store token
    Frontend->>API: GET /api/me
    API->>API: Validate JWT
    API->>DB: Load current user
    DB-->>API: User data
    API-->>Frontend: 200 OK + current user
    Frontend->>API: GET /api/workspaces
    API->>DB: Load user workspaces
    DB-->>API: Workspace list
    API-->>Frontend: 200 OK + workspaces
    Frontend-->>User: Display dashboard
